Blend raspberries in a food processor or blender. Pour mixture through a fine wire-mesh strainer, discarding seeds and pulp. Combine SPLENDA(R) No Calorie Sweetener with Fiber and cornstarch in a small saucepan; stir in raspberry puree. Bring to a boil over medium heat, stirring constantly; boil, stirring constantly, 1 minute. Chill. Spoon or drizzle 1 tablespoon raspberry sauce into each glass. Set aside. Process peaches, yogurt, milk, SPLENDA(R)(R) No Calorie Sweetener with Fiber, almond extract, and ice cubes in a blender until smooth, stopping to scrape down sides. Pour into glasses. Top with remaining raspberry sauce. Garnish, if desired. Serve immediately.